            include ../components/header.pug

            div.top__left
                img(src="img/top-left.svg" alt="")

            div.top__img
                img(src="img/top.svg" alt="")

            div.container
                div.top__content
                    h1.top__title Cryptocurrency
                    h2.top__subtitle Investing on Autopilot
                    p.text Bidgood is a customizable cryptocurrency trading bot that enables users to index the market, create custom portfolios, and automatically rebalance their cryptocurrency portfolios.
                    button.button Get started

        section.bot
            div.bot__img
                img(src="img/bot.svg" alt="")
                img(src="img/bot.png" alt="")
            div.container
                div.bot__content
                    h2.title Your Personal <br/>Crypto Trading Bot
                    p.text Grow your portfolio like the world's most sophisticated investors. We're making institutional portfolio management software available to everyone.
                    p.text.text--bold Bidgood is free to try for the first 7-days. A paid subscription starts at only $3/month.
                    button.button Get started

        section.steps
            div.container
                h2.title.title--center How to Get Started
                div.steps__flex
                    div.steps-item
                        div.steps-item__bg
                            img(src="img/step1.svg" alt="")
                        div.steps-item__content
                            img(src="img/step1-icon.svg" alt="")
                            p.steps-item__name Connect Exchange
                            p.steps-item__description Connect Bidgood  to your exchange. <br />API keys are securely encrypted <br />(HMAC SHA-256).
                    div.steps-item
                        div.steps-item__bg
                            img(src="img/step2.svg" alt="")
                        div.steps-item__content
                            img(src="img/step2-icon.svg" alt="")
                            p.steps-item__name Create or select strategy
                            p.steps-item__description Create a custom portfolio based <br />on advanced metrics or implement <br />an existing strategy.
                    div.steps-item
                        div.steps-item__bg
                            img(src="img/step3.svg" alt="")
                        div.steps-item__content
                            img(src="img/step3-icon.svg" alt="")
                            p.steps-item__name Automatically Rebalance
                            p.steps-item__description Bidgood keeps your portfolio <br />on track by automatically executing <br />portfolio rebalances.

                p.steps__note So you're new to Bidgood? No problem.
                button.button try it now

        section.pricing
            div.container
                h2.title.title--center Pricing
                p.pricing__description Bidgood pricing is tiered based on your portfolio size inorder to keep <br />our service affordable for those with smaller account sizes.

                div.pricing__flex
                    div.pricing-item
                        p.pricing-item__name Silver
                        p.pricing-item__price $<span>3</span>/month
                        p.pricing-item__label Account Value
                            strong Under $500
                        button.button Buy now
                    div.pricing-item.pricing-item--big
                        p.pricing-item__name Bronze
                        p.pricing-item__price $<span>6</span>/month
                        p.pricing-item__label Account Value
                            strong $500 - $1,000
                        button.button Buy now
                    div.pricing-item
                        p.pricing-item__name Gold
                        p.pricing-item__price $<span>14</span>/month
                        p.pricing-item__label Account Value
                            strong Over $1000
                        button.button Buy now

        section.methodology
            div.methodology__img
                img(src="img/methodology.svg" alt="")
                img(src="img/methodology.png" alt="")

            div.container
                p.title Cryptocurrency Indices
                p.text.text--bold Diversify Across the Entire Market with One Click
                p.text Diversification mitigates risk and improves returns. Studies found that 95% of active traders fail to beat the index. We built the HODL indices for users who want to diversify across the market instead of picking individual coins.
                button.button red methodology

            div.portfolios
                div.portfolios__img
                    img(src="img/portfolios.svg" alt="")
                    img(src="img/portfolios.png" alt="")
                div.container
                    div.portfolios__content
                        p.title Customized Portfolios
                        p.text.text--bold Create Portfolios with Advanced Market Metrics
                        p.text Select any coins, choose a weighting strategy, and see how it performed in the past. Use advanced market metrics to construct dynamic portfolios. You can also create a cryptocurrency index comprised of the top N coins.
                        button.button how it works

            div.rebalancing
                div.rebalancing__img
                    img(src="img/rebalancing.svg" alt="")
                    img(src="img/rebalancing.png" alt="")
                div.container
                    div.rebalancing__content
                        p.title Automatic Rebalancing
                        p.text.text--bold Rebalances Keep Your Portfolio on Track.
                        p.text When the market shifts, a portfolio will drift away from its target allocation. Bidgood  automatically rebalances your portfolio to keep it on track, saving you time. Portfolio rebalances generally lead to risk mitigation and improved returns.
                        button.button rebalancing study

            div.needs
                div.needs__img
                    img(src="img/needs.svg" alt="")
                    img(src="img/needs.png" alt="")
                div.container
                    div.needs__content
                        p.title Tailored to Your Needs
                        p.text.text--bold Customize HodlBot to Fit your Preferences.
                        p.text Change your rebalancing frequency, blacklist coins you want to avoid trading, liquidate your assets anytime. Bidgood is highly customizable. On top of that, we provide 24/7 customer support.
                        button.button Eхplore wiki

